    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次开局随机生成六边形地图，每一局都是完全不一样的挑战。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208260/extras/5fe3f805a2359f1cde693b88852784c4.poster.avif?t=1745388022\" width=560 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208260/extras/5fe3f805a2359f1cde693b88852784c4.webm?t=1745388022\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208260/extras/5fe3f805a2359f1cde693b88852784c4.mp4?t=1745388022\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >构筑自己的建筑物卡组，在地图上施展优秀的建造策略。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208260/extras/827030f5ba5c952ed86577987db46fb6.poster.avif?t=1745388022\" width=560 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208260/extras/827030f5ba5c952ed86577987db46fb6.webm?t=1745388022\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208260/extras/827030f5ba5c952ed86577987db46fb6.mp4?t=1745388022\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自由组合摩托车部件，搭配提升运送能力。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208260/extras/eca7ca2c1a0bcdb80f49cf9376dc7980.poster.avif?t=1745388022\" width=560 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208260/extras/eca7ca2c1a0bcdb80f49cf9376dc7980.webm?t=1745388022\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208260/extras/eca7ca2c1a0bcdb80f49cf9376dc7980.mp4?t=1745388022\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >综合卡牌，组件，地形，来应对最大的挑战。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208260/extras/ab27fdb5525078f7f61c358e68eac67f.poster.avif?t=1745388022\" width=560 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208260/extras/ab27fdb5525078f7f61c358e68eac67f.webm?t=1745388022\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208260/extras/ab27fdb5525078f7f61c358e68eac67f.mp4?t=1745388022\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
